script.name: !plugin.autotrade.getroute.docked
script.description: Autotrade - Get traderoute for dockedat's products

line.comment: * Gnasirator, 05.03.2012
* init
* Min profit
* 0: ware, 1: sellstation, 2: profit, 3: bool Rest ware found
* Check station products
* check every ware for sellstation and profit
* if ware is not in global array, skip it. could be illegal or otherwise useless
* script call has been updated for LU 1.3.5
* Fix: sellstation could be null, unknown, or in any other way not suitable
* Finally check buyamount against stored ship hardware
* Extra check: If sellstation is player-owned and bankrupt, blacklist it
* and search again for a sellstation
* NOTE: since blacklist is nonfunctional this doesn't work anymore, we would enter a infinite loop
* go to next ware instead
* append $station.sell to array $blacklist
* inc $i * <--- this statement would have retried the ware after blacklisting. Since no blacklist, can't retry either
* retry the same ware with another sellstation
* DON'T RETRY
* take used fuel into account
* better station found
* Array: Ware, Amount, Buystation, Sellstation, Profit, bSelling.Rest.Ware
